---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Words Containing NI — Scrabble Word List & Strategy"
  description="Complete list of Scrabble words containing NI with scores, definitions, and strategic tips. Master NI words for better Scrabble plays."
  keywords="scrabble words containing ni, ni words scrabble, words with ni, scrabble ni word list, ni scrabble strategy"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Words Containing NI — Scrabble Word List & Strategy",
    "description": "Complete list of Scrabble words containing NI with scores, definitions, and strategic tips.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-15",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/words-containing-ni" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring NI words in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Top NI words include TECHNIQUE (20 pts), KNITTING (13 pts), INFINITY (14 pts), UNIT (4 pts), and KNIGHT (14 pts). NI appears in 600+ valid Scrabble words." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How many Scrabble words contain NI?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Over 600 valid Scrabble words contain NI. Common examples include NICE, NIGHT, UNIT, FINISH, KNIGHT, KNITTING, INFINITY, and TECHNIQUE." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What strategy works best with NI tiles?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "NI is productive with 600+ words. The -TION/-NION patterns build bingos. NI- prefix words (NICE, NIGHT, NINE) give solid openers. The KNI- cluster (KNIT, KNIFE, KNIGHT) deploys the high-value K tile. UNI- words (UNIT, UNIQUE, UNION) are versatile mid-game plays." } }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">Letter Pair Content</span>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Words Containing NI — Scrabble Word List & Strategy</h1>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>4 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">NI is a productive letter pair appearing in over 600 valid Scrabble words. From everyday plays like NICE and NIGHT to premium targets like TECHNIQUE (20 pts) and KNIGHT (14 pts), NI combines well with high-value consonants. The KNI- cluster is particularly powerful for deploying the 5-point K tile, while UNI- words provide versatile mid-game options.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top NI Words by Score</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">#</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Word</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Points</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Definition</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">1</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">TECHNIQUE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">20</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A method of doing</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">KNIGHT</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">14</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A medieval warrior</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">3</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">INFINITY</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">14</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Without end</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">KNITTING</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Making fabric with yarn</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">FINISH</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To complete</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">KNIFE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A cutting tool</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">UNIQUE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">15</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">One of a kind</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">NIGHT</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">After sunset</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">UNION</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A joining together</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">NICE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Pleasant</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">UNIT</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A single thing</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">600+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid NI words</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">11 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Average score</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">Common</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Pair frequency</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips for NI Words</h2>

      <p>The KNI- cluster (KNIT, KNIFE, KNIGHT, KNITTING) deploys the valuable K tile efficiently. UNI- prefix words (UNIT, UNION, UNIQUE, UNIFORM) are versatile at any game stage. The -NISH ending (FINISH, VANISH, PUNISH) provides reliable hooks. TECHNIQUE (20 pts) is a strong bingo target using the QU pair. NI- prefix words (NICE, NIGHT, NINE, NIL) are quick plays when board space is limited.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">TECHNIQUE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">20 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">UNIQUE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">15 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">KNIGHT</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">INFINITY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">KNITTING</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">13 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">KNIFE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">12 pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Key Takeaway</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">NI offers <span class="text-white font-medium">600+ valid words</span> with strong synergy with high-value tiles. TECHNIQUE (20 pts) and UNIQUE (15 pts) are premium targets. KNIGHT (14 pts) and KNIFE (12 pts) efficiently deploy the K tile. Use UNI- words for versatile mid-game scoring.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/words-containing-qu" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words Containing QU — Essential Scrabble Q Words</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/words-with-multiple-vowels" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words With Multiple Vowels — Scrabble Vowel Dumps</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/four-letter-words-every-player-should-know" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Four-Letter Words Every Scrabble Player Should Know</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find every NI word from your tiles — instant results, no signup</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-gray-950 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
